            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-Hd1e108">Rubrica 8</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De castiate et pudicitia atque impudicitia</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-d1e114">
              De casti<!--line jumps down-->tate et pu<!--line jumps down-->dicitia</p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-d1e121">
              <lb ed="#C"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-Rd1e118">Theophrastus in aureo<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>la 
              tractatu de nup<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>tiis</ref> 
              <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-Qd1e127">Illa uero pudica est dicenda cui li<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>cuit 
              peccare sed noluit</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-d1e135">
              ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-Rd1e135">Yesus filius sirach in ecclesiastico 
              <lb ed="#C"/>capitulo 26</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-Qd1e139">fornicatio mulieris <unclear>etc.</unclear></quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-d1e148">
              ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-Rd1e150">Terentius 
              <lb ed="#C"/>in eutontumerumenon capitulo X</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-Qd1e152">Mulier compta et faceta hec 
              <lb ed="#C"/>est meretrix</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-d1e158">
              ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-Rd1e162">Ouidius sine titulo libro I 
              <lb ed="#C"/>capitulo 8</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-Qd1e162"></quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-d1e170">
              <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-Rd1e176"></ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-Qd1e174">Siqua metu dempto casta est 
              <lb ed="#C"/>ea denique casta que qua non liceat 
              <lb ed="#C"/>non facit ipsa facit ut iam seruans be<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>ne 
              corpus adultera mens est</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-d1e184">
              ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-Rd1e192">Quin<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>tilianus 
              <cb ed="#C" n="a"/>
              <lb ed="#C"/>2 declamatione</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-Qd1e188">Ergo si qua mihi est fides 
              <lb ed="#C"/>pudicitia etiam milite laudare eru<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>besco 
              feminarum est illa uirtus aliter 
              <lb ed="#C"/>mihi laudandus est uir fortis ydoneus 
              <lb ed="#C"/>bello promptus ad pericula praestantis animi</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-d1e200">
              <lb ed="#C"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-Rd1e210">Seneca ad lucillum XI epistolarum</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-Qd1e204">Plures 
              <lb ed="#C"/>pudore quam bona uoluntate uiri prohibiti 
              <lb ed="#C"/>abstinent</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-d1e212">
              ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-Rd1e225">Ualerius maximus libro 2 titulo I</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-Qd1e216">mas<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>silia 
              ciuitas <unclear>etc.</unclear></quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-d1e229">
              ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-Rd1e244">Lex autentici quomodo operet 
              <lb ed="#C"/>episcopos</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-Qd1e233"> qui non etas pudicia quam max<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>ime 
              mulieres ornat</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-d1e241">
              ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-Rd1e259">Marcialis cocus 
              <lb ed="#C"/>epigrammaton libro 4</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-Qd1e245">tanquam non liceat nulla pu<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>ella 
              negat</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-d1e255">
              ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-Rd1e275">Maximianus</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-Qd1e259">castus 
              <lb ed="#C"/>amor ueneris dicite quoque sitit</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-d1e265">
              ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-Rd1e287">Mon<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>tanarius 
              in luna cleri</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-Qd1e269">Res est difficilis castam 
              <lb ed="#C"/>bene ducere uitam nulla foret maior quam 
              <lb ed="#C"/>caste uiuere pena Sola namque suum fini<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>tur 
              morte duellum</quote>
            </p>
         </div>
